Package: ReporterScore
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Reporter Score-based Enrichment Analysis for Omics Data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R:
    person("Peng", "Chen",email ="pengchen2001@zju.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9449-7606"))
Description: The original reporter-score method comes from Patil, K. R. et al. PNAS 2005.
    In this package, we provide two reporter-score methods (mixed/directed) to get reporter-score for KEGG pathway or modules.
